### Authors

### Create an author
POST {{host}}/authors
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Jane Austen",
  "bio": "English novelist known for her six major novels.",
  "birthDate": "1775-12-16",
  "nationality": "British"
}

### Get all authors
GET {{host}}/authors

### (Optional) Set `authorId` variable
# After creating an author, copy the `_id` from the response and set `authorId` like:
# @authorId = <paste-id-here>

### Books

### Create a book
POST {{host}}/books
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Pride and Prejudice",
  "authorId": "{{authorId}}",
  "isbn": "9780141199078",
  "publishedDate": "1813-01-28",
  "pages": 432,
  "genre": "Fiction",
  "summary": "A classic novel about manners and marriage.",
  "rating": 4.5
}

### Get all books
GET {{host}}/books

### Get single book
GET {{host}}/books/{{bookId}}

### Update book
PUT {{host}}/books/{{bookId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Pride and Prejudice (Updated)",
  "authorId": "{{authorId}}",
  "isbn": "9780141199078",
  "publishedDate": "1813-01-28",
  "pages": 432,
  "genre": "Fiction",
  "summary": "Updated summary.",
  "rating": 4.6
}

### Delete book
DELETE {{host}}/books/{{bookId}}
